object.customQuery:
SELECT C.FullPolicyKey, 
A.PolicyKey, 
A.PolicyKeyCode, 
A.RiskId, 
A.CoverageId, 
A.CoverageCd, 
D.AgentCd, 
D.AgencyCd, 
A.ClaimNumber, 
B.ClaimType, 
A.MajorPerilCd, 
B.LossCauseCd, 
B.LossCauseDesc, 
B.SubLossCauseCd, 
A.AnnualStatementLineCd, 
A.StatLineCd, 
A.ReserveTypeCd, 
A.LossCoverageType, 
A.ReserveCd, 
A.ClassificationCd, 
A.ClaimantCd, 
A.ClaimantTransactionCd, 
A.PaymentTypeCd, 
B.LossDt, 
B.LossReportedDt, 
A.ClaimReopenDt, 
A.ClosedDt, 
A.ClaimantClosedDt, 
A.BookDt, 
A.CheckNumber, 
A.CheckDt, 
A.PayeeName, 
A.PayeeAddr1, 
A.PayeeAddr2, 
A.PayeeCity, 
A.PayeePostalCd, 
A.LossAccountEnteredDate, 
A.ClaimAddDt, 
CAST(A.TransactionNumber AS INTEGER) as TransactionNumber, 
A.TransactionUser, 
A.CatastropheNumber, 
C.GroupLine, 
A.ReserveChangeAmt, 
A.LossPaidAmt, 
A.LossSalvageAmt, 
A.LossSubrogationAmt, 
A.LossULAEExpense, 
A.LossALAEExpense, 
A.ClaimNumber, 
E.TransactionNumber, 
A.ReserveCd, 
A.RowEffEndDt, 
B.RowEffEndDt, 
D.RowEffEndDt, 
A.CheckAmt, 
F.PolicyKey, 
F.ClaimSystemId, 
LPAD(F.ClaimantNumber::VARCHAR, 3, '0') as ClaimantNumber, 
F.AssignedAdjusterName, 
F.RowEffEndDt, 
A.TaxAttachedInd, 
A.ProviderTypeCd, 
A.ProviderNumber, 
A.Required1099Ind, 
A.SubCoverageDesc, 
A.ReserveStatusCd, 
A.DeductibleRecovery
FROM dbo.claimTransaction A 
INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT losscausecd,
                          losscausedesc,
                          sublosscausecd,
                          claimnumber,
                          lossdt,
                          lossreporteddt,
                          claimtype,
                          RowEffEndDt
          FROM dbo.claimdetail
          WHERE roweffenddt = to_timestamp('9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'::text, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MI:SS'::text)
            AND claimstatuscd <> 'Deleted'
          ) B
          ON A.claimnumber::text = B.claimnumber::text
INNER JOIN dbo.PolicyDetail C  ON A.PolicyKey = C.PolicyKey
LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT DISTINCT AgentCd
		,AgencyCd
		,RowEffEndDt
	FROM dbo.Agents
	WHERE RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
) D ON C.ProviderNumber = d.AgentCd
LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT ClaimNumber
		,MIN(CAST(TransactionNumber AS INTEGER)) AS TransactionNumber
	FROM dbo.ClaimTransaction
	WHERE ReserveCd = 'Indemnity'
		AND roweffenddt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
	GROUP BY ClaimNumber
) E ON A.ClaimNumber = E.ClaimNumber
LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT policykey
		,ClaimSystemId
		,ClaimantNumber
		,AssignedAdjusterName
		,RowEffEndDt
	FROM dbo.ClaimantDetail
	WHERE AssignedAdjusterName IS NOT NULL
		AND RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.0000000'
) f ON a.PolicyKey = f.PolicyKey
	AND a.ClaimSystemId = f.ClaimSystemId
	AND cast(a.ClaimantCd AS INT) = f.ClaimantNumber
WHERE A.roweffenddt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
